These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Food: grapes, orange, avocado, cucumber
Nationality: brazilian, french, pakistani, polish
1. Nationality:french is on the left of Nationality:brazilian##1
2. Food:grapes == Nationality:polish##1
3. Nationality:pakistani is on the right of Nationality:brazilian##1
4. Food:orange is on the left of Nationality:polish##1
5. Food:cucumber is on the left of Nationality:brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | cucumber | avocado | orange | grapes   |
| Nationality   | french  | brazilian     | pakistani   | polish |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Hobby: fishing, dancing, magic-tricks, hiking
Sport: badminton, cricket, golf, weightlifting
1. Hobby:hiking == Sport:cricket##1
2. Hobby:fishing is on the far right##1
3. Hobby:dancing is on the right of Hobby:hiking##1
4. Hobby:hiking is on the right of Sport:golf##1
5. Sport:cricket is on the left of Sport:badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | hiking | dancing | fishing    |
| Sport   | golf    | cricket      | badminton | weightlifting |

 #################################
 
