5. Hobby:filmmaking is on the left of Movie-Genre:satire##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | chess | reading | filmmaking   | camping |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure   | spy | documentary | satire         |

