2. Music-Genre:dubstep is on the right of Music-Genre:funk##1
3. Beverage:cola is on the right of Beverage:7up##1
4. Beverage:juice is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:almond-milk == Music-Genre:funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | juice | almond-milk  | 7up | cola |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | funk | dubstep           | classical   |

